Zero $ startup

Most clinics will not start to see meaningful revenue during the first 3 months. It makes financial sense to keep costs to a minimum during this period. Our remote staffing model will allow you to pay based on a model that is easily scalable for a fraction of the cost.

Linear scaling

Even after you reach operational profitability, you will still benefit from a linearly scaling model as you continue to grow. This model avoids fixed staffing costs and suboptimal staff utilization.

Lower costs

Performing administrative tasks in-office can be expensive especially when you add in taxes and non payroll costs. If you utilize our staff in India or the Philippines, you could save up to 75% of your costs. Staffing locally in the US does not save you costs, but will allow you other benefits listed here.

Phone lines

Deciding which vendor to use as your phone provider. We can set up your phone line and setup extensions and configure your desk phones.

Scheduling

We act as your receptionist and our staff will handle all incoming calls related to scheduling including new appointments, reschedules and cancellations. We can also make outbound calls to the patients if you need us to.

Virtual Assisting

We can manage your eligibility verifications, respond to emails or chat.

Medical Assistant

We can call to get prior authorizations for tests and procedures or make referrals. We will handle inbound calls regarding refill requests and can also make outbound calls regarding lab requests.

Fax

We will manage all incoming faxes and attach them to the correct patient chart and set appropriate tasks. Our staff will also set up new patients for any referrals and enter lab results.
